      <title>Matery主题的修改与优化</title>
      <link href="/matery-change/"/>
      <url>/matery-change/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>记录主题的优化与修改</p><a id="more"></a><h3 id="主题修改"><a href="#主题修改" class="headerlink" title="主题修改"></a>主题修改</h3><p>修改<code>index-cover.ejs</code>文件</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//调整主页轮播图左右转跳的两个箭头显示相对背景圈圈偏上</span></span><br><span class="line">#prev-cover i {</span><br><span class="line">        margin-top: <span class="number">5.5</span>px;<span class="comment">//添加，让主页左跳按钮箭头下移</span></span><br><span class="line">    }</span><br><span class="line">#next-cover i {</span><br><span class="line">    margin-top: <span class="number">5.5</span>px;<span class="comment">//添加，让主页左跳按钮箭头下移</span></span><br><span class="line">    }<span class="comment">//将主页显示的“readstart”按钮修改为“enter blog”</span></span><br><span class="line">&lt;i <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"fa fa-angle-double-down"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="regexp">/i&gt;&lt;%- __('enter Blog') %&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>修改<code>footer.ejs</code>文件</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//将bg-color标签修改为footer-bg</span></span><br><span class="line">&lt;footer <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"page-footer footer-bg"</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//注释掉总访问前的竖杠</span></span><br><span class="line">&lt;span id=<span class="string">"busuanzi_container_site_pv"</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;!-- | --&gt;&amp;nbsp;<span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">i</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"far fa-eye"</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">//删除网站运行时间的秒数，将“本站运行时间”修改为“本站已苟活”</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">if (startYear == todayYear) {</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">    document.getElementById("year").innerHTML = todayYear;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">    document.getElementById("sitetime").innerHTML = "本站已苟活 " + diffDays + " 天 " + diffHours +</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">        " 小时 " + diffMinutes + " 分钟 ";//+ diffSeconds + " 秒";</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">  } else {</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">    document.getElementById("year").innerHTML = startYear + " - " + todayYear;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">    document.getElementById("sitetime").innerHTML = "本站已苟活 " + diffYears + " 年 " + diffDays +</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">    " 天 " + diffHours + " 小时 " + diffMinutes + " 分钟 ";//  + diffSeconds + " 秒";</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">    }</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>修改<code>matery.css</code>文件</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">/* 新建标签手机菜单上背景 */</span></span><br><span class="line">.mobile-bg{</span><br><span class="line">    background:rgb(<span class="number">221</span>, <span class="number">221</span>, <span class="number">221</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    opacity: <span class="number">0.9</span>;</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/* 新建标签页尾背景 */</span></span><br><span class="line">.footer-bg{</span><br><span class="line">    background:url(https:<span class="comment">//s1.ax1x.com/2020/07/11/U1pjW6.png);</span></span><br><span class="line">}</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/* 修改nav背景 */</span></span><br><span class="line">.bg-color {</span><br><span class="line">    background:rgba(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0.3</span>)</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/* 修改网页下方进度指示条的颜色 */</span></span><br><span class="line">.progress-bar {</span><br><span class="line">    background: linear-gradient(to right, #ffffff 0%, #000000 100%);</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/* 修改删除如下属性以移除主页轮播图的遮蔽效果 */</span></span><br><span class="line">.bg-cover:after {</span><br><span class="line">.bg-cover:before,</span><br><span class="line">.bg-cover:after {</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/* 修改回到顶部按钮背景 */</span></span><br><span class="line">.top-scroll .btn-floating {</span><br><span class="line">background: rgba(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0.3</span>);</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/* 手机界面侧边栏头像位置调整为居中 */</span></span><br><span class="line">header .side-nav .mobile-head img {</span><br><span class="line">    margin-top: <span class="number">30</span>px;</span><br><span class="line">    margin-left: <span class="number">70</span>px;</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/* 手机界面侧边栏名字位置调整为居中，字体颜色为黑色 */</span></span><br><span class="line">header .side-nav .mobile-head .logo-name {</span><br><span class="line">margin-top: <span class="number">-30</span>px;</span><br><span class="line">margin-left: <span class="number">70</span>px;</span><br><span class="line">color: rgba(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/* 手机界面侧边栏签名调整为居中，字体颜色为黑色 */</span></span><br><span class="line">header .side-nav .mobile-head .logo-desc {</span><br><span class="line">    color: rgba(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    text-align: center;</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>修改<code>bg-cover-content.ejs</code>文件</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//将主页副标题下的轮播文字修改为每日一诗，但是要将`subtitle:false`才能生效</span></span><br><span class="line">&lt;% } <span class="keyword">else</span> { %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;!-- &lt;%= config.description %&gt; --&gt;<span class="comment">//注释掉先前的</span></span><br><span class="line">    &lt;%- <span class="string">'&lt;span id="jinrishici-sentence"&gt;正在加载今日诗词....&lt;/span&gt;'</span> %&gt;<span class="comment">//修改为每日一诗的语句块</span></span><br><span class="line">&lt;% } %&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>修改<code>header.ejs</code>文件</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//去掉PC界面logo旁的头像</span></span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- &lt;% <span class="keyword">if</span> (theme.logo !== <span class="literal">undefined</span> &amp;&amp; theme.logo.length &gt; <span class="number">0</span>) { %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;img src=<span class="string">"&lt;%- theme.jsDelivr.url %&gt;&lt;%- url_for(theme.logo) %&gt;"</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"logo-img"</span> alt=<span class="string">"LOGO"</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;% } %&gt; --&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>修改<code>mobile-nav.ejs</code>文件</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//修改手机界面侧边菜单签名</span></span><br><span class="line">&lt;div <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"logo-desc"</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;% <span class="keyword">if</span> (config.description &amp;&amp; config.description.length &gt; <span class="number">0</span>) { %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;%= config.description %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;% } <span class="keyword">else</span> { %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    不是吧，不是吧？真有人看我的博客？</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;% } %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;<span class="regexp">/div&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="regexp">/</span><span class="regexp">/修改背景标签，将bg-color标签改为mobile-bg</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="regexp">&lt;div class="mobile-head mobile-bg"&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>修改<code>back-top.ejs</code>文件</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//将回到顶部的按钮修改为fa-angle-double-up向上箭头与ENTER BLOG的a-angle-double-down向下箭头同款</span></span><br><span class="line">&lt;i <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"fa fa-angle-double-up"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="regexp">/i&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><!-- rebuild by neat --><script>        document.querySelectorAll('.github-emoji')          .forEach(el => {            if (!el.dataset.src) { return; }            const img = document.createElement('img');            img.style = 'display:none !important;';            img.src = el.dataset.src;            img.addEventListener('error', () => {              img.remove();              el.style.color = 'inherit';              el.style.backgroundImage = 'none';              el.style.background = 'none';            });            img.addEventListener('load', () => {              img.remove();            });            document.body.appendChild(img);          });      </script>]]></content>
      
      
